        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-198",
        "content": "If she felt such confidence in my good intentions, and could suppose it to be only a mistake, why should you be so ready to take offence?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
